MPUMALANGA police have launched a manhunt for Tichana Nyamunda who is wanted for allegedly stealing money from Takealot at Emalahleni. According to Captain Eddie Hall, the suspect reportedly stole parcels and cash from Takealot offices at Emalahleni in December 2022 when he was acting as the manager of the shop. REGISTER TO COMMENT! “Please take note that there is a reward of R20 000 for information that can lead to the arrest of the suspect,” said Hall. Anyone with information that can assist the cops is asked to call Detective Sergeant Zwidi Ngwenya on 082 849 3562 or CrimeStop on 08600 10111.